paragraphs.title: Top 100 brands
paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
with cte as (
select brand, count(distinct subOrderId) as sold 
from `all(agCmDump)` where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000))) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 group by brand)
select brand, sold from cte order by sold desc limit 100
",1000)
